\id 2JN - Zyphe 
\h 2 JOHAN 
\toc1 JOHAN CAKUA UIHNINGNAH 
\toc2 2 JOHAN 
\toc3 2 Jh 
\mt1 JOHAN 
\mt2 CAKUA UIHNINGNAH 
\c 1  
\s1 Kih tlenah 
\p  
\v 1 Khrisaw macang a cangpaw kama tah thingpaw canuno le a sawtei sahlo khatah ma ca heh ka ca kua he. Biahmuisui letah ca do he neh ka, kama long cang lytah Khazing biahmuisui aa hnihpaw cawngsaw vytei zong tah aa ca do he.  
\v 2 Zecawtamaw tatah biahmuisui cawh kaa chung letah hring ka, chaizaw tah kaaning khatah a ung paria thlangnah cawtah khei kaa ca do he. 
\p  
\v 3 Paw a cangpaw Khazing le a Sawcapaw Zisu Khri taitei ningdonah le zawngenah le thlawlungnah cawh biahmuisui le doná tah kaaning khatah a ung leimei thlang a. 
\p  
\v 4 Paw tei bia a ma pehpaw hratah na sawtei leh thaikhehpaw cawh biahmuisui letah a ung he tahpaw thui neh ka, ka thaw a chah ngetei.  
\v 5 Taico dopaw canuno, atoheh nama khatah biapeh a thapaw ka ciapaw cang lytah a thoning taitah kaa hnui thahpaw biapeh khah a cang. Pakheh le pakheh a do he peh takhah ka ca sia he.  
\v 6 Mataico ma heh donah cawh a cang. A bia pehpaw nge tah kaa hringpaw khah a cang. Athoning taitah na thui thahpaw hrakhei a biapeh cawh donah letah naa hring ruapaw a cang. 
\p  
\v 7 Hinghepaw a hlupui khazaw letah chuh myca he ka, Zisu Khri cawh mehnung pung tah a va chuhpaw a cang takhah a zing lypaw sahlo a cang he. Ma hapaw cawngsaw cawh dungkhei a thaipaw, Khri carae cawh a cang he.  
\v 8 Naa hrehnangpaw khah naa hly ly nápawtah a raering my lo. Naa lahsong tlangtling teitah naa hmuh ná pawtah teria my lo.  
\v 9 Ahohmai Khri cawngpahnah letah ung paria thlang ly tei a khunghlui laipaw cawh Khazing aa hnui lypaw a cang he. Ma cawngpahnah chung letei a ung thlangpaw cawh Paw kha Sawcapaw kha aa hnui pakawh he.  
\v 10 Pakheh kheh tah ma cawngpahnah he a tle ly tei naaning khatah a vong caco naa ing letah tlungsah khe la, reikaw chaw zong tah chai hrah khe lo.  
\v 11 Ma hapaw cawngsaw tlung ing a pa-awngpaw cawh ma cawngsawpaw a suanah letah aa hrong hrahpaw a cang. 
\p  
\v 12 Nama khatah a hlupui ciapaw ka hnui naná teitah catla le catui hmang cawh du bei neh. Ma navy co, kaa lunglawngnah a tling khy nápawtah va ca tlong he tei, hmedai teitah bia a ruapaw heh ka hnabei a suipaw a cang. 
\p  
\v 13 Thing ciapaw naa sateino a sawtei sahlo tah naa kih aa ca tle he.